{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_10_01_short",
  "title": "天動瑠依 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年始特番の二週間前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bicycle-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1439.9999857,
          "startTime": 1.4399999857
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……ラストスパート……！\n……ふぅ、これで今日のトレーニングは終わりね",
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え、{user}さん？　いつからそこに？\nすみません、集中していて気付かなくて",
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "フィットネスバイク、お疲れ様\n朝から漕いでたけど、まさかずっと漕いでいたのか？",
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "途中で一度、休憩しました\nでも『挑戦』の本番では、休憩なんて出来ませんから",
      "startTime": 28.5999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二週間後の、新年の特番でやる『挑戦』企画か……\n瑠依は、人力飛行機で飛ぶんだよな",
      "startTime": 37.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、失敗する訳にはいきませんから\nそれに、本番では空で漕ぐんです",
      "startTime": 44.2666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "天候や風向きだって影響するでしょうし\n練習とは、全然違うはずですから……",
      "startTime": 50.5666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "だから練習では、本番の何倍も漕げるように\n鍛えておきたいんです",
      "startTime": 57.2999993642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5526.666666700003,
          "startTime": 62.8266660309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "丸一日、トレーニングに専念出来るのは\n今日が最後ですし――",
      "startTime": 61.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……お、お腹の音が、こんなに大きく鳴るなんて……\n……すみません、お昼ご飯、食べ忘れてました",
      "startTime": 69.9333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}